What you need to know:

Kenya Basketball Federation women’s Commission Publicity and Marketing, Pamela Sinda challenged the athletes to share their ordeals.  The  Committee members on Gender Welfare in Sports are Catherine Ndereba – Chairperson, Rose Wasike (Committee Administrator), Dr. Kizzie Shako (Secretary), Hibo Hussein (Joint Secretary), Prof. Paul Ochieng, Catherine Mabwi, Ibrahim Hussein, Linda Ndiwa and Ted Kwaka.